author: deweese
msg: 1) Updated the Apache License on a few files that seemed to have
slipped through the cracks so far.
2) Fixed new-line endings on some files.

author: deweese
msg: 1) Pretty Printing is now an option when saving the current document to disk.
2) Rhino will now turn off 'optimization' when it can't create a classloader.
Allows JavaScript to run in an applet context.
3) The 'init.svg' document that is rendered as part of Squiggle loading
should now render quicker.
4) Updated some javadocs myself.
5) Fixed bug #34210, element selectors are now case sensitive.
6) Fixed bug #34213, important properties are respected.
7) Fixed a JDK 1.4ism (svgbrowser.Main).
8) Updated security tests in light of number 2 above.
9) Fixed a small bug in the SVGONLoadException security test.

author: cam
msg: 1. Added methods to expose rgbColor and iccColor properties
from CSSOMSVGColor objects, per the SVG 1.1 ECMAScript binding.

author: cam
msg: 1. Updated a few remaining old Apache licences.
2. Various javadoc fixes, resulting in no more warnings when
building the javadocs.
